  "title": "Class Teacher (English)",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Responsibilities</u></p><ul><li>Plan, prepare and deliver English programme according to the school curriculum guidelines</li><li>Conduct fun learning activities and use appropriate teaching methods according to the children age and learning abilities</li><li>Maintain an effective classroom management, respectful learning environment and well organised routine care duties</li><li>Prepare class newsletters and maintain student progress reports</li><li>Plan and execute school events</li><li>Communicate and maintain good rapport with parents and colleagues</li></ul><p><u>Job Requirements</u></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Early Childhood Care and Education</li><li>Teaching certificate in English language for young children</li><li>At least 2 years of relevant teaching experience </li><li>Commitment and dedication to support children early childhood development</li><li>Able to work independently and in a team</li></ul><p>Working Hours : 8.00am - 4.30pm</p><p>Working Days : Monday – Friday, ad-hoc trainings and events according to school schedule</p><p>Interested applicants please submit a resume & a recent photograph by email to -> <strong>admin@jks.com.sg</strong></p>",
